{"word":"προερύω","slug":"προερύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n87416\" key=\"proeru/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">προερύω</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ aor.\">aor.</a></tns> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-έρυσσα</foreign> (v. infr.), <sense id=\"n87416.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">draw on</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">forward,</tr_> in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> always of ships, </sense> <sense n=\"1\" id=\"n87416.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νῆα θοὴν ἅλαδε προέρυσσεν</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drew</tr_> the swift ship <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">forward,</tr_> by hauling her from the beach to the sea, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:308\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.308</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπὴν ἅλαδε προερύσσω</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νῆας</foreign>) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:358\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.358</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n87416.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">move</tr_> the ship <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">forward,</tr_> by rowing her towards the shore, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">αὐτὰς δ᾽ ἐσσυμένως προερύσσαμεν ἤπειρόνδε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:73\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.73</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὴν δ᾽ εἰς ὅρμον προέρυσσαν ἐρετμοῖς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:435\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.435</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:15:497\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.497</biblScope> </bibl> (but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">προερεσσ-</foreign> was rightly written by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristarch.</author> </bibl> and others).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}